        <item>
            <title>AirPods Pro 2 放進盒裡時常發出輕微異響？蘋果證實此為功能而非故障</title>
            <description>&lt;figure class=&quot;caas-figure&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;caas-figure-with-pb&quot;&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;caas-img-container&quot;&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;caas-img has-preview&quot; alt=&quot;AirPods Pro 2 放進盒裡時常發出輕微異響？蘋果證實此為功能而非故障&quot; src=&quot;https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2024-09/972ce1a0-7463-11ef-a82f-3a43deec9576&quot; referrerpolicy=&quot;no-referrer&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;caption-wrapper caption-aligned-with-image&quot;&gt;&lt;figcaption class=&quot;caption-collapse&quot;&gt;AirPods Pro 2 放進盒裡時常發出輕微異響？蘋果證實此為功能而非故障&lt;/figcaption&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;p&gt;在把 AirPods Pro 2 塞進耳機盒後，你是否會經常聽到一些輕微異響？不用擔心這不是什麼故障，蘋果已經證實裝置發聲是為了確定麥克風和揚聲器能正常運作。「為了確保你的 AirPods 麥克風和揚聲器處於最佳運作狀態（比如能盡可能準確地提供聽力測試結果），當耳機被放到充電盒內時，它們可能會定期發出輕微的響聲。」蘋果在&lt;a data-i13n=&quot;cpos:1;pos:1&quot; href=&quot;https://support.apple.com/en-gb/guide/airpods/devd9aac5b42/web&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-ylk=&quot;slk:官方支援資料;cpos:1;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas&quot; class=&quot;link &quot;&gt;官方支援資料&lt;/a&gt;中如此寫道。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;所以説，如果之前你有因為這一情況感到困擾的話，至少蘋果現在給出了一個確切的説法。除了這樣的「日常維護」發聲外，AirPods 在電量告急、開始充電時其實也會發出響聲。其中一些聲音在耳機連上手機後可以被關掉，有此需要的用家去設定裡關掉「啟用充電盒聲音」選項即可。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;緊貼最新科技資訊、網購優惠，追隨 Yahoo Tech 各大社交平台！&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;🎉📱 Tech Facebook：&lt;a data-i13n=&quot;cpos:2;pos:1&quot; href=&quot;https://www.facebook.com/yahootechhk&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-ylk=&quot;slk:https://www.facebook.com/yahootechhk;cpos:2;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas&quot; class=&quot;link &quot;&gt;https://www.facebook.com/yahootechhk&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;🎉📱 Tech Instagram：&lt;a data-i13n=&quot;cpos:3;pos:1&quot; href=&quot;https://www.instagram.com/yahootechhk/&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-ylk=&quot;slk:https://www.instagram.com/yahootechhk/;cpos:3;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas&quot; class=&quot;link &quot;&gt;https://www.instagram.com/yahootechhk/&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;🎉📱 Tech WhatsApp 社羣：&lt;a data-i13n=&quot;cpos:4;pos:1&quot; href=&quot;https://chat.whatsapp.com/Dg3fiiyYf3yG2mgts4Mii8&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-ylk=&quot;slk:https://chat.whatsapp.com/Dg3fiiyYf3yG2mgts4Mii8;cpos:4;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas&quot; class=&quot;link &quot;&gt;https://chat.whatsapp.com/Dg3fiiyYf3yG2mgts4Mii8&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;🎉📱 Tech WhatsApp 頻道：&lt;a data-i13n=&quot;cpos:5;pos:1&quot; href=&quot;https://whatsapp.com/channel/0029Va91dmR545urVCpQwq2D&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-ylk=&quot;slk:https://whatsapp.com/channel/0029Va91dmR545urVCpQwq2D;cpos:5;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas&quot; class=&quot;link &quot;&gt;https://whatsapp.com/channel/0029Va91dmR545urVCpQwq2D&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;🎉📱 Tech Telegram 頻道：&lt;a data-i13n=&quot;cpos:6;pos:1&quot; href=&quot;https://t.me/yahootechhk&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-ylk=&quot;slk:https://t.me/yahootechhk;cpos:6;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas&quot; class=&quot;link &quot;&gt;https://t.me/yahootechhk&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
